          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Blanks needed</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">For extra Z tiles</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">The 40+ Point Legends</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 #1</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">PIZZAZZY</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">49 points • 8 letters • SOWPODS only • Z×3</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The theoretical highest-scoring single word by base tile value in SOWPODS. Requires both blanks as Z substitutes (reducing real score to ~29 pts). Still legendary when achievable.</p>
      </div>

